---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p class="long-form">
      Statecraft Systems is the institutional vehicle for building and carrying an operative tradition of good rule. The tradition is alive because it is enacted.
    </p>
    <div class="rule"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Operative Tradition</h2>
    <div class="production-card">
      <div class="structural-marker"></div>
      <p>
        We are not a consultancy with a philosophy. We are an operative tradition in formation. The tradition is operative because the disciplines are practiced, not merely referenced. Formation transmits capability through direct work, not curriculum. The tools are built and used, not just described. The web grows through enacted reciprocity, not membership lists. Each person who does the work and builds something real becomes a carrier of the tradition.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Background</h2>
    <div class="production-card">
      <div class="structural-marker"></div>
      <p>
        The practice is led by Moritz Bierling. The work draws on over four years of direct involvement in agent orchestration, multi-model systems, and frontier tooling. The capability is technical and structural. The approach is direct contact with the material, honest assessment, and skilled making.
      </p>
      <a href="https://moritzbierling.com" class="production-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">moritzbierling.com</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Formation Lineage</h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Exosphere</h3>
        <p>Multi-week to two-month intensive formations. Learning through direct immersion in reality and the building of operative capacity.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Volta</h3>
        <p>Weekend retreats structured around shared challenge and the transmission of capability in condensed timeframes.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Modern Minuteman</h3>
        <p>Structured cohort programs teaching Natural Law disciplines and civic resilience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="production-card" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <div class="structural-marker"></div>
      <p>
        This lineage is maintained and expanded through the pursuit of Structural Consultant certification, ensuring the disciplines are practiced with structural soundness and rigor.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <h2>Initiate Contact</h2>
    <p class="long-form">
      Engagement begins with a direct conversation to assess structural fit.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" class="production-link">Reach out</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
